VPS Specs: Processor Speed- 1.98 GHz RAM- 1344MB Disk Space- 59 GB Bandwidth- 1050 GB cPanel + VZ
*DDoS Protection

Rules: * No DDoSing/DoSing * No Trolling/Spamming/Flaming * No Glitching (invisibility, noclip, spawning/duping) * Respect Staff * Donators are not staff. I’m choosing mods of my choice, or else, they donated for it. * If someone asks you to not PJ, you don’t have to listen. Massing is allowed.
Those are all information, please check out and add my msn if your interested, anthonydukaj@live.com
Thanks, Anthony Formerly "DynastyRSPS"
